data.description: All brick end unit townhouse/duplex that offers a 1st floor family room addition recently remodeled with recessed lighting and wood laminate floors, newer windows and sliding glass door leading to nice sized fenced backyard and a newer shed . Kitchen has oak cabinets and granite countertops newer Fridge, Stove, black SS . Recessed lighting in living room and dining room with hardwood floors. Upstairs has two Bedrooms and a full bath . Five windows recently replaced . Newer water heater . Basement partially finished newer washer .Close to Public Transportation shopping and Canty school. Seller will offer 5,000.00 closing cost credt for Buyer to buy down mortgage.
